OL,3,C'Misogyny' of former journalist who
OL,4,Charassed women
OL,6,FA former newspaper reporter has
OL,7,Favoided an immediate prison sentence
OL,8,Fafter admitting harassing four women
OL,9,Fincluding former colleagues.
OL,11,FRobert Sutcliffe, 56, from
OL,12,FHuddersfield, sent a stream of
OL,13,Fmessages to the women over a seven-
OL,14,Fmonth period, including telling one he
OL,15,F"could have her put in a car in half
OL,16,Fan hour".
OL,18,FHe later described himself as "the
OL,19,Fmost famous man in Huddersfield".
