OL,3,C'Misogyny' of former journalist who
OL,4,Charassed women
OL,6,FSutcliffe's solicitor told Leeds
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court: "It is impossible
OL,8,Fto get away from the sexism running
OL,9,Fthrough this case."
OL,11,FThe court was told how Sutcliffe, a
OL,12,Fformer Yorkshire Post and Bradford
OL,13,FTelegraph and Argus reporter, was
OL,14,Fworking for the Huddersfield Examiner
OL,15,Fand its associated website Yorkshire
OL,16,FLive when he targeted colleague
OL,17,FAbigail Marlow with a series of
OL,18,Fmessages and tweets.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/17
