OL,3,C'Misogyny' of former journalist who
OL,4,Charassed women
OL,6,FProsecutor Charles McCrerae said Ms
OL,7,FMarlow had been mentored by Sutcliffe,
OL,8,Fbefore he turned nasty.
OL,10,FMr McCrerae said Sutcliffe emailed her
OL,11,Fin June last year "criticising her
OL,12,Fwork".
OL,14,FHe said: "That was the first time she
OL,15,Fhad seen that side to him and did feel
OL,16,Fbullied but dismissed it at the time".
OL,18,FBut on another occasion Ms Marlow
OL,19,Freceived "20 plus messages" from
OL,20,FSutcliffe, where his "tone had
OL,21,Fchanged".
