OL,6,FIn another message, he said: "I think
OL,7,Fwe need to put our friendship out of
OL,8,Fits misery".
OL,10,FHe also referenced "romantic walks in
OL,11,Fthe snow" when their relationship was
OL,12,Fsaid to have never been romantic.
OL,14,FMs Marlow told Sutcliffe not to
OL,15,Fcontact her again but he ignored the
OL,16,Frequest.
