OL,6,FSutcliffe also put an image of Ms
OL,7,FMarlow on his Twitter page and was
OL,8,Farrested, interviewed and given a
OL,9,Fcaution with conditions not to contact
OL,10,Fher or post about her on social media.
OL,12,FHowever, he breached the order "almost
OL,13,Fimmediately" when he posted on Twitter
OL,14,Fabout his experience in custody.
