OL,3,C'Misogyny' of former journalist who
OL,4,Charassed women
OL,6,FThe court heard that Ms Preston and
OL,7,FSutcliffe had a disagreement at work
OL,8,Fafter he refused a request relating to
OL,9,Fa piece of work.
OL,11,FSutcliffe sent messages to Ms Preston
OL,12,Fsaying she "didn't know what she was
OL,13,Fdoing" and disparaging her ability in
OL,14,Fher role. Mr McCrerae said: "He
OL,15,Fsuggested she had been over-promoted
OL,16,Fand would seek to expose her."
