OL,3,C'Misogyny' of former journalist who
OL,4,Charassed women
OL,6,FSutcliffe was suspended from work in
OL,7,FAugust last year following an
OL,8,Fallegation of gross misconduct.
OL,9,FFollowing his suspension, Sutcliffe
OL,10,Fmessaged Ms Preston to say: "What a
OL,11,Fmess you made, old girl."
OL,13,FHe later posted a picture on Twitter
OL,14,Fof Ms Preston, comparing the size of
OL,15,Fher breasts to her intelligence.
OL,17,FMr McCrerae said Sutcliffe had
OL,18,F"bombarded" Ms Preston with messages
OL,19,Fand tweets for two weeks.
