OL,3,C'Misogyny' of former journalist who
OL,4,Charassed women
OL,6,FSome tweets were posted in the early
OL,7,Fhours of the morning and included
OL,8,Fpictures of Ms Preston. She described
OL,9,Fthe messages and tweets as having
OL,10,F"misogynistic undertones" and said she
OL,11,Ffelt the situation had escalated
OL,12,F"because I am a woman".
OL,14,FIn her victim impact statement, Ms
OL,15,FPreston said the messages only stopped
OL,16,Fwhen she "declared herself as a
OL,17,Fvictim".
