OL,3,C'Misogyny' of former journalist who
OL,4,Charassed women
OL,6,FMr McCrerae said: "At home she didn't
OL,7,Ffeel safe - he knows the town she
OL,8,Flives in. The worst aspect was being
OL,9,Fpublicly degraded and him writing
OL,10,Fabout the size of her breasts."
OL,12,FMr McCrerae told the court Sutcliffe
OL,13,Fhad also targeted two staff members
OL,14,Fworking at his local pub, The Plumbers
OL,15,FArms.
OL,17,FHe sent them identical messages
OL,18,Fbetween 10 and 11 November last year
OL,19,Fclaiming he could "get people to put
OL,20,Fthem in a car in half an hour anywhere
OL,21,Fin the world".
