OL,6,FThe prosecutor said both knew
OL,7,FSutcliffe from the pub - with one
OL,8,Fdescribing him as "strange". It was
OL,9,Falso said he was a "heavy drinker" who
OL,10,Fwould drink three or four pints an
OL,11,Fhour.
OL,13,FIn one message he said: "You're a
OL,14,Fworld class user, you need to have a
OL,15,Flong hard look at yourself. You have
OL,16,Fan attractive streak but you have
OL,17,Fother qualities."
