OL,3,C'Misogyny' of former journalist who
OL,4,Charassed women
OL,6,F"During this part of his life it was
OL,7,Fspiralling out of control while he was
OL,8,Fin the depths of a mental health
OL,9,Fcrisis."
OL,11,FHe added: "It is impossible to get
OL,12,Faway from the sexism running through
OL,13,Fhis case but he says in his life he
OL,14,Fhas wishes to support women."
OL,16,FDistrict Judge Hollins said a
OL,17,Fprobation worker undertaking
OL,18,FSutcliffe's pre-sentence report
OL,19,Fdescribed him as "entitled" and said
OL,20,Fhe had told her he is "the most famous
OL,21,Fman in Huddersfield".
