OL,6,F"The deficit in your thinking skills
OL,7,Fand in your misogyny is, in my view,
OL,8,Fclear," he said.
OL,10,FSutcliffe was given a 24-week prison
OL,11,Fsentence suspended for 18 months.
OL,13,FRestraining orders, prohibiting him
OL,14,Ffrom contacting all four victims
OL,15,Fdirectly or indirectly, posting about
OL,16,Fthem on social media or attending The
OL,17,FPlumbers Arms in Huddersfield were
OL,18,Falso made for three years.
